          h5#sub-tag-text Don't settle for a house.<br>Fall in love with a place you call <em>home</em>. 

  .expert-section
    .row
      .small-12.columns.no-padding
        .headshot
        h2 Trust a true upstate expert
        .small-12.medium-6.large-4.columns
          h5 Neighborhoods
          p 
            | A home is more than square footage and a floor plan. The place you live is the neighborhood, the people and quality of life. From downtown condos to suburban communities and acreage, Susan has decades of local knowledge about the Upstate giving you a perspective you can not see through online research.
        .small-12.medium-6.large-4.columns
          h5 Schools
          p 
            | Finding a great home doesn't mean it's zoned for great schools. Each family has different educational needs and finding the right school can make all of the difference. Having lived in many of the major school districts herself, Susan can help you find a wonderful home and the best school for your children. 
        .small-12.medium-6.end.large-4.columns
          h5 Destination Homes
          p 
            | Upstate South Carolina is surrounded by incredible natural beauty, on display in lakes, mountains and open country. If you're looking for a scenic home or second home, Susan's knowledge of the Upstate's landscape will serve as your guide to finding a gorgeous destination called home. 
