  .services#services
    .row
      .small-12.columns.no-padding
        h2.text-center Services
        .small-12.medium-9.medium-centered.column
          p.text-center.border-line 
            | Whether you are buying, selling, or renting, you can rest assured you are taken care of with Susan's full-service representation and professionalism. 
        .small-12.medium-6.columns
          h5 Buying<span>?</span> 
          p
            | Susan will meet, listen, and assist you in finding a place to call home. She provides: 
          ul
            li Current information (updated hourly) on available properties new construction advisory services
            li Custom, real-time email notifications for each client
            li Comparable analysis for properties and neighborhoods
            li Contract scribing and negotiations
            li Inspections, contractor and closing attorney referrals
            li New construction advisory services
        .small-12.medium-6.columns
          h5 Selling<span>?</span> 
          p 
            | Selling a home doesn't have to be a difficult process, and the right realtor makes all the difference. Susan provides: 
            ul
              li Current market analysis
              li Comparable sales analysis and history
              li Comparable pricing information and history and 
              li Trusted referrals for appraisals, inspections and warranties 
              li Access to world-class staging services
        .small-12.end.columns
          h5 Renting<span>?</span> 
          p 
            | Need a temporary home or waiting to buy<span>?</span> Looking to get away and enjoy a relaxing home on one of the many mountains or lakes in the Upstate<span>?</span>  Susan will find you the right house, town home, condo, or apartment to meet your short or long term needs. Whether you are relocating temporarily, or just need a weekend away to travel and see your favorite team on the road, let Susan find you the right place so you have time to relax.

