  .relocation#relocation
    .row
      .small-12.medium-5.medium-push-7.columns
        h2 Medical Relocation 
        .circle-photo
      .small-12.medium-7.medium-pull-5.columns
        p
          | Upstate South Carolina's booming healthcare economy is creating an influx of transplants to the area. Finding the right movers, temporary housing, doctors, insurance and other personal services makes relocation a daunting task. Susan is approved by all major relocation companies worldwide and with her vast network and local knowledge, she will make your transition to the area enjoyable and effortless. 

  .about#about
    .row
      .small-12.medium-5.columns
        h2 About Susan
        .circle-photo
      .small-12.medium-7.columns
        p
          | Susan has been involved with the business of real estate (residential and commercial) for over 25 years in Florida, Michigan, North Carolina and South Carolina. Growing up in a family of real estate developers, this business is in her blood and she lives for it! Susan has served on several community boards over the last 20 years and is a sustaining member of the Junior League of Greenville, where her last active placement was Community Vice President. Whether you are looking for residential, vacation homes, relocation, investments or commercial properties, Susan can assist you. 

